snippet.title: Prison Architect 2 - Coming March 26th! | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
📣 Welcome, Architects!
Design and develop your own personalized penitentiary in Prison Architect 2. The classic prison-builder will soon break out into 3D, and it's up to you to contain it!

👆 Pre-Order on Steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/1257610/
📖 Learn More https://pdxint.at/PA2Website
🗨️ Discuss https://pdxint.at/PA2pdxforum

✅ Join our communities:
TikTok — https://pdxint.at/PATikTok
X (Formerly Twitter) — https://twitter.com/PrisonArchitect
Facebook — https://www.facebook.com/PlayPrisonArchitect
Reddit (Fanrun) — https://www.reddit.com/r/prisonarchitect/
Discord (Fanrun) — https://discord.com/invite/prisonarchitect
